Hi Samantha,

Thank you for the remote session!

As we spoke we did the following:
- we increased the number of items displayed on all pages from: Device Control -> Global Settings -> Maximum no. of records returned in a report search from 200 to 5000.
- we checked again and the Computers we delete are now deleted from the computers list.
- unfortunately we do not have an automatic deletion setting for computers that are Offline and Unlicensed, but you can use the below filter to search for them:


We will leave this ticket open a few more days to make sure that everything is okay.
